NTP

1) Configure Master with NTP service--see masterconf branch ntp.conf
2) Configure Minion with NTP client--see minion branch ntp.conf
3) Change time manually on Master and see if time changes on the Minion and vice versa
4) Have NTP Autostart on boot
#systemctl list-unit-files
#systemctl enable ntpd.service

5) Check listening ports of the NTP service
#systemctl status ntpd



6) Where is the config file located?---/etc/ntp.conf
